Company Overview of Spearhead Capital, LLC



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Spearhead Capital, LLC, a financial services firm, focuses on providing customized solutions to family offices. It specializes in sourcing alternative investment opportunities by working with investment managers in various regions and countries, such as the United States, Asia, China, India, Japan, Africa, and Europe, as well as investment managers focused on strategies in structured credit, liquid credit, deep value equities, activist, and private equity. The company also develops fixed income and other strategies to enable family offices to achieve a range of investment objectives; and identifies and arranges for the purchase of appropriate securities. In addition, it offers private placem...
Spearhead Capital, LLC, a financial services firm, focuses on providing customized solutions to family offices. It specializes in sourcing alternative investment opportunities by working with investment managers in various regions and countries, such as the United States, Asia, China, India, Japan, Africa, and Europe, as well as investment managers focused on strategies in structured credit, liquid credit, deep value equities, activist, and private equity. The company also develops fixed income and other strategies to enable family offices to achieve a range of investment objectives; and identifies and arranges for the purchase of appropriate securities. In addition, it offers private placement insurance product support services, including the design, implementation, customization, and usage of insurance dedicated fund and investment management services, as well as administration and product maintenance services. Further, the company provides investment banking services that include buy side and sell side mergers and acquisitions, raising growth capital, access to the capital markets for debt and equity financing, venture capital investing and due diligence support, strategic turnarounds and growth financings, and financial restructuring. Furthermore, it offers merger advice services that include corporate sales, divestitures, and mergers and acquisitions; private capital raising; restructuring and recapitalizations; and financial advisory for privately held and publicly traded companies, as well as private equity firms. Spearhead Capital, LLC was formerly known as Spearhead, LLC and changed its name to Spearhead Capital, LLC in 2009. Spearhead Capital, LLC is based in Wellington, Florida.
